# Ignore everything by default
*

# Allow repo metadata
!.gitignore

# Allow prompt-only skill pack
!.skills/
!.skills/chinese-novelist/
!.skills/chinese-novelist/SKILL.md
!.skills/chinese-novelist/CHANGELOG.md
!.skills/chinese-novelist/DEPRECATIONS.md
!.skills/chinese-novelist/GETTING-STARTED.md
!.skills/chinese-novelist/INTEGRATION-ARCHITECTURE.md

!.skills/chinese-novelist/prompts/
!.skills/chinese-novelist/prompts/**

!.skills/chinese-novelist/references/
!.skills/chinese-novelist/references/**

!.skills/chinese-novelist/workflows/
!.skills/chinese-novelist/workflows/**

!.skills/chinese-novelist/schemas/
!.skills/chinese-novelist/schemas/**

!.skills/chinese-novelist/data/
!.skills/chinese-novelist/data/**

# Keep these excluded even if someone runs `git add -A`
.skills/chinese-novelist/tools/
.skills/chinese-novelist/scripts/
.skills/chinese-novelist/automation/
.skills/chinese-novelist/benchmarks/
.skills/chinese-novelist/.claude/

# Typical cruft
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.bak-*
